  <brief_title>Comparison of Tissue Retractors During Cesarean Delivery in Obese Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of the Efficacy of the Mobius ™ Retractor in Performing Cesarean Sections in Patients With BMI ≥35kg/m2</official_title>
  <sponsors>
